snippet.title: Bober Bros' The Hole - Official Teaser Trailer | The Indie Horror Showcase 2024
snippet.description: Watch the unsettling teaser trailer for Bober Bros' The Hole, an upcoming first-person horror game that explores the cracks in domestic life. Your neighbor’s drilling starts the nightmare, but the holes reveal dark secrets far deeper than any wall could hide. No cheap scares, only disturbing reality. Bober Bros The Hole will be available on PC.
